ement on the\ncomputational times compared to the classical deterministic framework at the\nexpense of a moderately small approximation error.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Mar 2019 20:03:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 Mar 2019 08:17:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 19 Jul 2019 16:44:03 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2019 17:24:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-30"}
