 a wealth of information on\nthe three currently known planets and have the potential to reveal additional\nplanets in the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2019 14:26:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 May 2019 22:50:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
